listitem.para:
Burst Depth - Source temporal pattern burst depth. This is the
            total depth the original pattern had, patterns are given in percentages and not original
            depths;

AEP (source) - The source temporal pattern AEP at the location
            it was recorded. This AEP is based of the 2016 IFDs and the burst depth of the
            event;

Storm IL is approximately equal to Pre-burst – In
            the case where storm IL and pre-burst are close to equal IL is satisfied and no IL needs
            to be taken from the burst temporal pattern;
